Biasanya dia kelihatan begitu sombong dan menyebalkan.

257
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,480
sekarang dia berbaring di sini dengan tenang.

258
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:13,170
saya rasa agak tidak biasa.

259
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,680
Adakah anda keluarga Shen Jianjun?

260
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,040
Ya.

261
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,280
Dia telah selesai menjalani rawatan kecemasan.

262
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:29,140
Anda boleh masuk dan bercakap dengannya sekarang.

263
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:30,960
Ayah.

264
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,680
Bagaimana keadaan ayah?

265
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,680
sudah lebih baik?

266
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,400
Anda.

267
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,250
Anda ingin mencari Wen Tao?

268
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:45,960
Enam puluh ribu.

269
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,400
Pong.

270
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,610
Kad ini benar-benar...

271
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,320
Hei.

272
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,490
Shen Wentao.

273
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:54,640
Ayah sakit.

274
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:56,120
Dia ingin kamu datang melihatnya.

275
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:56,880
Saya sibuk.

276
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:57,600
Saya tidak ada masa untuk datang.

277
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,930
Adakah kamu masih mempunyai hati nurani?

278
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,280
Sakit.

279
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,040
Menyusahkan sepanjang hari.

280
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,120
Cepatlah.

281
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,200
Siapa yang begitu menyusahkan?

282
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:07,960
Kakak saya.

283
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,560
Ayah.

284
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,320
Shen Wentao.

285
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,640
Ada urusan hari ini.

286
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,770
Tidak dapat datang.

287
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:22,620
Anda terus berehat dan pulih di sini.

288
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,250
Nan Feng.

289
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,560
Kenapa?

290
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:57,600
Kamu gila ke?

291
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,960
Ayah masih terbaring di hospital.

292
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:01,020
Kamu berani bermain mahjong di sini.

293
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,810
Shen Wentao.

294
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,260
Kamu masih manusia ke?

295
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,040
Saya tidak ada wang.

296
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,920
Apa yang boleh saya lakukan di hospital?

297
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,480
Gila.

298
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,080
Apa kaitannya dengan ada wang atau tidak?

299
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:12,280
Ini adalah kewajipan yang harus dilakukan.

300
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,520
Saya tidak seperti kamu.

301
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,960
suka berlakon drama sedih seperti ini.

302
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,290
Saya.

303
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,520
Jika kamu beri saya wang,

304
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:20,450
saya akan pergi ke hospital dengan kamu sekarang juga untuk berbakti.

305
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,240
Kamu berani pukul saya?

